        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1828753846" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1416807241911843502">The brutal truth of poverty in America is far more devastating than any fiction ever could be. In evicted, Matthew Desmond brings rigorous sociological research and ethnography to Milwaukee&apos;s inner city. This book is painful and necessary and eye opening. I am ashamed of how little I knew about poverty and eviction. This book is fucking depressing and hopeless and excellent. We have got to do better. Also the segregation! And racist ass Ned who made his biracial stepdaughters say &quot;white power&quot; w</span>
  <span id="freeText1416807241911843502" style="display:none">The brutal truth of poverty in America is far more devastating than any fiction ever could be. In evicted, Matthew Desmond brings rigorous sociological research and ethnography to Milwaukee's inner city. This book is painful and necessary and eye opening. I am ashamed of how little I knew about poverty and eviction. This book is fucking depressing and hopeless and excellent. We have got to do better. Also the segregation! And racist ass Ned who made his biracial stepdaughters say "white power" while their mom hoped it wouldn't scar them. What???</span>
  <a data-text-id="1416807241911843502" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

