          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;it is hard to argue that housing is not a fundamental human need. Decent, affordable housing should be a basic right for everybody in this country. The reason is simple: without stable shelter, everything else falls apart.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
